Title: Temozolomide and Sunitinib Malate in Treating Patients With Stage III or Stage IV Malignant Melanoma
Conditions: Metastatic Melanoma
Phase: PHASE1
Status: COMPLETED
Primary outcomes: Maximum tolerated dose of sunitinib malate when administered concurrently with temozolomide (Phase I); Overall safety; Response rate as assessed by modified RECIST criteria (phase II)